sql:
SELECT page_rank
FROM node_centrality
WHERE network_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
PageRank centrality is a measure of a node's influence within a network; 
A network with at least one node is considered an active network. 
A community in this context could be a group of densely connected nodes within a network.

